                <note rend="inline" type="source">838.51/2757: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Armour</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-12-08T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 8, 1933—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>88. Your 135, December 7, 1 p.m. The Department’s No. 83 of December 1 and No. 85
                    of December 4 transmitted to you all the information we have received to
                    date.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
